# Data Dictionary

| Variable | Type | Description | Business Relevance |
| Trans_ID | String | Unique Transaction Identifier | Track individual sales |
| Cust_ID | String | Unique Customer Identifier | Link transactions to specific users |
| Date | Datetime | Date of Purchase | Analyze sales trends over time |
| Amount | Float | Gross Transaction Value | Calculate Revenue and ROI |
| Category | String | Product Department | Identify top-performing product lines |
| Cust_DOB | Datetime | Customer Date of Birth | Demographic segmentation |
| Status | String | Order Fulfillment State | Monitor logistics and return rates |
| Customer_Age | Integer | Calculated Age (2026 - DOB) | Target marketing by age group |
